Subject: [PATCH 233/233] Validate GLM DSA native top-k compact decode

---
 tests/test-llama-archs.cpp | 47 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----
 1 file changed, 42 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

diff --git a/tests/test-llama-archs.cpp b/tests/test-llama-archs.cpp
index ed2ae7005..482ae2faf 100644
--- a/tests/test-llama-archs.cpp
+++ b/tests/test-llama-archs.cpp
